        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-9">
                <div class="image-wrapper"><div class="image_style" style="width:96%;"><picture><source sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*6sDUTAbKX_ICVVAjunCo3g.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*6sDUTAbKX_ICVVAjunCo3g.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*6sDUTAbKX_ICVVAjunCo3g.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*6sDUTAbKX_ICVVAjunCo3g.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*6sDUTAbKX_ICVVAjunCo3g.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*6sDUTAbKX_ICVVAjunCo3g.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*6sDUTAbKX_ICVVAjunCo3g.png 1400w" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*6sDUTAbKX_ICVVAjunCo3g.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*6sDUTAbKX_ICVVAjunCo3g.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*6sDUTAbKX_ICVVAjunCo3g.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*6sDUTAbKX_ICVVAjunCo3g.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*6sDUTAbKX_ICVVAjunCo3g.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*6sDUTAbKX_ICVVAjunCo3g.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*6sDUTAbKX_ICVVAjunCo3g.png 1400w"/><img alt="" loading="lazy" role="presentation" src="https://miro.medium.com/max/700/1*6sDUTAbKX_ICVVAjunCo3g.png"></picture></div><p class="mbr-description mbr-fonts-style mt-2 align-center display-12 text-muted" style="font-size:12px;">Arrows represent the derivative at the corresponding points</p><br></div></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">If we initialize randomly the network, we are putting any random point on this curve (let’s say <strong>w=3</strong>) . The learning process is actually saying this:</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">- Let’s check the derivative.<br></br>- If it is positive, meaning the error increases if we increase the weights, then we should decrease the weight.<br></br>- If it’s negative, meaning the error decreases if we increase the weights, then we should increase the weight.<br></br>- If it’s 0, we do nothing, we reach our stable point.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">In a simple matter, we are designing a process that acts like gravity. No matter where we randomly initialize the ball on this error function curve, there is a kind of force field that drives the ball back to the lowest energy level of ground 0.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-9">
                <div class="image-wrapper"><div class="image_style" style="width:93%;"><picture><source sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 680px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*dvgzK4beVXBGBELDXP9JpA.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*dvgzK4beVXBGBELDXP9JpA.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*dvgzK4beVXBGBELDXP9JpA.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*dvgzK4beVXBGBELDXP9JpA.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*dvgzK4beVXBGBELDXP9JpA.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*dvgzK4beVXBGBELDXP9JpA.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1360/format:webp/1*dvgzK4beVXBGBELDXP9JpA.png 1360w" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 680px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*dvgzK4beVXBGBELDXP9JpA.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*dvgzK4beVXBGBELDXP9JpA.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*dvgzK4beVXBGBELDXP9JpA.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*dvgzK4beVXBGBELDXP9JpA.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*dvgzK4beVXBGBELDXP9JpA.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*dvgzK4beVXBGBELDXP9JpA.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1360/1*dvgzK4beVXBGBELDXP9JpA.png 1360w"/><img alt="" loading="lazy" role="presentation" src="https://miro.medium.com/max/680/1*dvgzK4beVXBGBELDXP9JpA.png"></picture></div><br></div></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
